<b><big><a name="CppAD Configuration Files" id="CppAD Configuration Files">CppAD Configuration Files</a></big></b>
<br/>
In the table below, 

<code><i><font color="black"><span style='white-space: nowrap'>builddir</span></font></i></code>
 is the build directory; i.e., the directory where
the CppAD
<a href="installunix.xml#Configure" target="_top"><span style='white-space: nowrap'>Configure</span></a>
 command is executed.
The directory 
<code><i><font color="black"><span style='white-space: nowrap'>prefix</span></font></i></code>
 is the value of
<a href="cmake.xml#cmake_install_prefix" target="_top"><span style='white-space: nowrap'>cmake_install_prefix</span></a>
