The directory 
<code><i><font color="black"><span style='white-space: nowrap'>datadir</span></font></i></code>
 is the value of
<a href="cmake.xml#cmake_install_datadir" target="_top"><span style='white-space: nowrap'>cmake_install_datadir</span></a>
